step.tex:
      \begin{align}
     \dfrac{dV}{dT} &= 8\text{ cm$^3$/s}\\
     \text{But as } V&= L^3, \frac{dV}{dT} = \frac{d}{dT}L^3 \\
     &= 3L^2\cdot\frac{dL}{dT} \\ 
     \implies \left[\dfrac{dL}{dT}\right]_{L=12} &= 
     \dfrac{8\frac{cm^3}{s}}{3\cdot\text{(12 cm)}^2} = \frac{1}{54}\text{ cm/s}
\end{align}
